          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Employee Profit-Sharing Encouragement Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to prohibit certain employers from deducting the compensation of highly compensated individuals unless the employer makes profit-sharing distributions to employees during the year. </p>]]></text>
